name: ANCESTORS: Great Great Great
description:
Featuring Elvis (who is 1/16 native american) and honouring his Great Great Great Grandmother, Morning White Dove. You can see where The King got his good looks from.

70cm X 100cm, on Fabriano paper, hand-printed by the artist at Ink Spot Press, with Jane Sampson. 

Limited edition of 30. 

This is a labour of love, including fluorescent orange background scratches, Cherokee Indian patterning in Phthalo Blue, Turquoise in torso and heart area, Blue black ink 'pop art' style half-tone for Elvis and his Great Great Great Grandmother & Gold Lines linking the two together. 

This print works well both ways up. 

All prints are packaged with care and are currently sent with a few extras, usually cards, stickers and experimental prints. 

FREE POSTAGE & PACKAGING ANYWHERE IN THE WORLD
